    public class ExprPrinter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExprVisitor
    Created by Daniele on 26/04/2017. This ExprPrinter Class Pretty Prints and Evaluates the input. Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division For every arithmetic expression, according to mathematics precedence rule, the input pretty prints and evaluation applied to given input
